name: Crystalline Mist Leapheart
text: Leapheart, the crystalline evolution of the Smokehopper, emerged resplendent. Its refractive body caught moonbeams, casting prismatic light through the forest. The creatures stood in awe as the Smokehopper's joyful spirit found new expression in Leapheart’s dance, leaving a shimmering, stardust wake beneath the ever-watchful, luminous celestial orb.
